<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation - AutoXpress</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .order-details {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .agent-info {
      background: #e3f2fd;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">ðŸš— AutoXpress</div>
      <p>Premium Automotive Parts & Service</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Thank you for your order, <%= @customer.name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>We've received your order and are preparing it for shipment. Here are your order details:</p>
      
      <div class="order-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Order Number:</span>
          <span><strong>#<%= @order.order_number %></strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Order Date:</span>
          <span><%= @order.order_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Product:</span>
          <span><%= @order.product_name %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Vehicle:</span>
          <span><%= @order.car_year %> <%= @order.car_make_model %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Product Price:</span>
          <span>$<%= number_with_precision(@order.product_price, precision: 2) %></span>
        </div>
        <% if @order.tax_amount > 0 %>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Tax:</span>
          <span>$<%= number_with_precision(@order.tax_amount, precision: 2) %></span>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <% if @order.shipping_cost > 0 %>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Shipping:</span>
          <span>$<%= number_with_precision(@order.shipping_cost, precision: 2) %></span>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span>Total Amount:</span>
          <span>$<%= number_with_precision(@order.total_amount, precision: 2) %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="agent-info">
        <h4>Your Sales Agent</h4>
        <p><strong><%= @agent.email.split('@').first.humanize %></strong> is handling your order and will keep you updated throughout the process.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>We'll process your order within 1-2 business days</li>
        <li>You'll receive a shipping notification with tracking information</li>
        <li>Estimated delivery: <%= @order.estimated_delivery&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") || "2-5 business days" %></li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Questions about your order? Reply to this email or call us at <strong>(555) 123-AUTO</strong>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>AutoXpress</strong> - Premium Automotive Parts</p>
      <p>This email was sent regarding order #<%= @order.order_number %></p>
      <p>Â© <%= Date.current.year %> AutoXpress. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>